      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi, <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/wave.png?v=12\" title=\":wave:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wave:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>We are working on an improved version of the calendar on <a href=\"https://monday.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>. With “Calendar it” you will be able to view activities by month, week and day in greater detail and in a more attractive way. We invite you to discover our prototype.</p>\n<p>Link: <a href=\"https://acortar.link/sT4U0d\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://acortar.link/sT4U0d</a></p>\n<p>Do you like it? You can sign up for our wishlist to be among the first to know when we have our first release. Likewise, we will be very grateful for the feedback you can give us.</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/7/7565460dc3b60bbea9b695148e1383e1bf111b6a.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />\n\n      <a href=\"https://forms.monday.com/forms/cd99a102684c1a5156ebc0c1de917dce?r=use1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">forms.monday.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img src=\"https://dapulse-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/v1645260315/monday-forms/Frame_1261156053.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" />\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://forms.monday.com/forms/cd99a102684c1a5156ebc0c1de917dce?r=use1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Calendar It - whishlist | WorkForms</a></h3>\n\n  <p>From requests, feedback to data collection and more. Turn your insights into action with customizable WorkForms.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/4/a4dd97c8dd76be7151b792c54c6f56f856127a0c.png\" title=\"Calendar 1_\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/a/4/a4dd97c8dd76be7151b792c54c6f56f856127a0c_2_620x500.png\" alt=\"Calendar 1_\" width=\"620\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Calendar 1_</span><span class=\"informations\">872×703 63.4 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/b/7bc6d49bbf21ec312357da9183cfa9f4ef51991e.png\" title=\"Calendar 2_\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/b/7bc6d49bbf21ec312357da9183cfa9f4ef51991e_2_628x500.png\" alt=\"Calendar 2_\" width=\"628\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Calendar 2_</span><span class=\"informations\">878×699 58.3 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/d/bdd93d85e480842c7d96158fcee24cc3e4f293a0.png\" title=\"Calendar 3_\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/d/bdd93d85e480842c7d96158fcee24cc3e4f293a0_2_624x500.png\" alt=\"Calendar 3_\" width=\"624\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Calendar 3_</span><span class=\"informations\">877×702 49.4 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>"
